quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  50,30,"On the Day He says to Hell, ´Are you full?´ it will ask, ´Are there no more to come?´"
  50,31,"And the Garden will be brought up close to those with taqwa, not far away"
  50,32,´This is what you were promised. It is for every careful penitent
  50,33,those who fear the All-Merciful in the Unseen and come with a contrite heart
  50,34,Enter it in peace. This is the Day of Timeless Eternity.´
  50,35,They will have there everything they want and with Us there is still more
  50,36,How many generations before them We destroyed who had greater force than them and scoured many lands! Did they find any way of escape
  50,37,"There is a reminder in that for anyone who has a heart, or who listens well, having seen the evidence"
  50,38,"We created the heavens and the earth, and everything between them, in six days and We were not affected by fatigue"
  50,39,So be patient in the face of what they say and glorify your Lord with praise before the rising of the sun and before it sets
  50,40,And glorify Him during the night and after you have prostrated
  50,41,Listen out for the Day when the Summoner shall call out from a nearby place
  50,42,"The Day they hear the Blast in truth, that is the Day of Emergence"
  50,43,It is We who give life and cause to die and We are their final destination
  50,44,"The Day the earth splits open all around them as they come rushing forth, that is a gathering, easy for Us to accomplish"
  50,45,"We know best what they say. You are not a dictator over them. So remind, with the Qur´an, whoever fears My Threat"